node.text:
[Janggut Laksa] - Got my Laksa craving satisfied with @janggut_laksa .

Takeaway and island wide delivery is available, order at http://janggutlaksa.oddle.me/
.
minimum order has been lowered to $35, with a flat $6 delivery fee.
U making craving for laksa, look very delicious 🤤
Thank you ! Glad you loved it! ❤️Stay Safe ! 😊
